    "description": "&quot;《钻石之手：登上月球（Diamond Hands: To The Moon）》是一款玩法简单，但很难掌握的跳跃平台游戏，最终目标是登上月球。玩家通过向左、向右移动和跳跃来控制角色—非常简单。通过练习，你可以锻炼跳跃技巧（通过控制跳跃的力度）并在任何目标平台上着陆。登上月球的猿猴不仅能够获得钻石之手的称号，还能获得想要的一切！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727810/extras/13836592ac3be3f5d051be1eaca8dd5e.poster.avif?t=1750767139\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727810/extras/13836592ac3be3f5d051be1eaca8dd5e.webm?t=1750767139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727810/extras/13836592ac3be3f5d051be1eaca8dd5e.mp4?t=1750767139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br> 一只猿猴意味着……弱小！<br> 为那些寻求最具挑战性冒险的玩家提供单人模式。<br> <br> 猿猴团体意味着……强大！<br> 与最多10个好友一起合作进行游戏。可使用公共和私人在线服务器。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727810/extras/0338137f4c3146802f29b680aac38bd4.poster.avif?t=1750767139\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727810/extras/0338137f4c3146802f29b680aac38bd4.webm?t=1750767139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727810/extras/0338137f4c3146802f29b680aac38bd4.mp4?t=1750767139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br> 打破记录<br> 挑战全世界最棒的速跑选手，在名人堂中占有一席之地！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727810/extras/5176e71a43b24f5ea24286fd6bf9a316.poster.avif?t=1750767139\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727810/extras/5176e71a43b24f5ea24286fd6bf9a316.webm?t=1750767139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727810/extras/5176e71a43b24f5ea24286fd6bf9a316.mp4?t=1750767139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br> 本游戏是模拟发生在Reddit与华尔街战争中的事件。游戏的场景，和不断变化的主题呈现了新手在第一次掌握股票交易时可能经历的投资阶段。共有10个不同的场景，其中包括：<br> - 证券交易所<br> - 游戏<br> - 蜡笔之地<br> - 暗池<br> - FUD（恐惧、不确定和怀疑）<br> - 鸡汤之地（+梅奥）<br> - +其他4个场景（我们不会剧透惊喜！）<br><br> <br> 声明：游戏不提供金融建议，我们只是热爱股票。&quot;",
